<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: slideIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #45a049;
        }

        /* Button Style */
        .btn {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s, color 0.3s; /* Added color transition */
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: #fff; /* Changed text color on hover */
        }

        /* Animation */
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>This is our Spotify-like app. Here you can play song, make a playlist, add a liked song and many more things.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing us.</p>
